I can make observations about the Cylons, their physical condition,

24
00:01:19,410 --> 00:01:24,290
带回关于让你们都在恐惧的病毒的信息
bring back information about this disease which now threatens all of you.

25
00:01:24,370 --> 00:01:25,910
你知道这是什么吗?
