我和你一样困惑
I am just as baffled as you are.

32
00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:52,520
就如那份手稿所写 
RACETRACK: Just like the scriptures say.

33
00:01:52,610 --> 00:01:56,360
就在那里  狮头星云  还有闪耀的眼睛
There it is, the Lion's Head nebula and the Blinking Eye.

34
00:01:57,610 --> 00:02:00,360
