是 长官
MARINE: Yes, sir.

61
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,480
好的 我准备连入数据库
ATHENA: Okay, I'm gonna try to call up the database.

62
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:24,780
如果我能联接上 把固体继电器导入那边的液体中
If I get a connection, put the SSR leads in the water over there.

63
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:28,490
降低错误检校级别 来扩大数据传输带宽
Reduce the error correction levels for highest throughput.

64
00:05:35,710 --> 00:05:37,460
你确定想这么做吗?
RACETRACK: You sure you wanna do that?

65
00:05:37,540 --> 00:05:39,000
就这么做了
ATHENA: It's how it works.

66
00:05:48,930 --> 00:05:50,390
你还好吗?
You okay?

67
00:05:53,140 --> 00:05:55,980
还好  数据库已经差不多都损坏了
Yeah. The data points are almost completely corroded.

68
00:05:56,060 --> 00:06:00,020
我不知道我能够得到什么信息 但我会试的
I don't know if I'm gonna get much out of here, but let's try.

69
00:06:08,110 --> 00:06:10,450
进行得怎么样了?
What is going on?

70
00:06:10,530 --> 00:06:13,120
已进入所有防御带
MARINE: We're now inside all perimeters.

71
00:06:16,460 --> 00:06:19,080
妈的! 这个还活着呢!
Frak me! This one's alive!

72
00:06:19,170 --> 00:06:21,920
这儿! 我们找到个活的!
We got a live one over here!

73
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,920
丹利 彼得斯 掩护大家!
MATHIAS: Danelli, Peters, cover the Major!

74
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,050
他们是活的!
APOLLO: They're alive!

75
00:06:26,130 --> 00:06:30,760
卡拉狄加 我是阿波罗 我们找到1 2 3 4 
Galactica, Apollo. We've got one, two, three, four,

76
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,850
5个活的赛昂人
five living skin jobs down here.

77
00:06:32,930 --> 00:06:35,390
我重复一次 5个活着的
I say again, five... Five living.

78
00:06:36,100 --> 00:06:37,310
你们开火了吗?
HELO: Are you taking fire?

79
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:39,350
没有 没有
Negative, negative.

80
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,850
他们看起来状况不妙
They seem in pretty bad shape.

81
00:06:40,940 --> 00:06:43,270
不要大意 如果他们有什么危险举动
Don't take any chances. If they make any threatening moves...

82
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,650
相信我吧
APOLLO: You can trust me on that one.

83
00:06:45,730 --> 00:06:47,110
趴下
MARINE: Stay down!

84
00:06:47,190 --> 00:06:49,990
上尉  我们该怎么办?  要把他们带出去吗?
Major, what do we do? Should we take them out?

85
00:06:50,070 --> 00:06:52,660
不要开火 不要开火!
APOLLO: Hold your fire. Hold your fire!

86
00:06:55,990 --> 00:06:57,410
别动 妈的
MATHIAS: Stay, you frakkers!

87
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:59,830
我说了别开火!
I said hold your fire!

88
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:07,710
赐予我们...力量...智慧...
NO. 6:Grant us the strength, the wisdom.

89
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,760
他们在干什么呢?
APOLLO: What are they doing?

90
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:11,970
最重要的...承诺的量度
Above all, a measure...

91
00:07:12,050 --> 00:07:14,930
嗨 雅典娜 你在干什么?  雅典娜!
Hey, Athena, what are you doing? Athena!

92
00:07:15,010 --> 00:07:17,390
你在干什么?  雅典娜!
What are you doing? Athena!

93
00:07:17,470 --> 00:07:20,480
赐予我们...力量...智慧...
Grant us the strength, the wisdom...

94
00:07:25,860 --> 00:07:27,440
叛徒
Traitor.

95
00:07:30,780 --> 00:07:32,610
拯救你自己吧
Save yourself.

96
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:33,740
从何说起?
From what?

97
00:07:34,530 --> 00:07:36,370
离我们远点
Keep away from us.

98
00:07:36,990 --> 00:07:38,450
这儿发生什么了?
What happened here?

99
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:43,710
一个信标 我们把它带上船了
NO. 6: The beacon, we brought it onboard.

100
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:48,550
它有病毒
It carried a disease.

101
00:07:50,630 --> 00:07:52,720
我们被感染了
We're infected.

102
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,470
感染?
Infected?

103
00:07:55,550 --> 00:07:56,510
噢 他妈的!
Son-of-a-bitch!

104
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,680
行了 行了 行了! 
Okay, okay, okay!

105
00:07:57,760 --> 00:08:00,270
冷静下来!
Settle down, keep your heads!

106
00:08:00,350 --> 00:08:03,060
看好门 看好门!
Watch the doorways! Get the doorways!

107
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:09,730
卡拉狄加  我是阿波罗  我们这儿有个状况
Galactica, Apollo. We have a situation down here.

108
00:08:13,990 --> 00:08:17,070
那些赛昂人感染了一种病毒
The Cylons have been infected with a disease.

109
00:08:18,410 --> 00:08:22,750
我们都暴露在这里了 我们都暴露在这里了
We have all been exposed. We've all been exposed.

110
00:09:24,020 --> 00:09:26,850
他们登船后一定要执行隔离程序
COTTLE: They'll have to come aboard under quarantine procedures.

111
00:09:26,940 --> 00:09:29,810
从机库里清理出一条路通到医务室 并要消毒
Clear a path from the hangar deck to sickbay and sterilize it,

112
00:09:29,900 --> 00:09:31,230
而猛禽机跟随他们后面进来
and the Raptors after they're in.

113
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,900
就交给我处理
I'll handle that.

114
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:34,740
他们要隔离多长时间呢?
How long will they have to stay in quarantine?

115
00:09:34,820 --> 00:09:36,150
在血检结果出来前  我也不知道要多长时间
I won't know that until I do the blood work.

116
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:38,610
可能几天或几星期  这是没法说的事情
Could be days, weeks, there's no way to tell.

117
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:40,990
你说他们是被那个信标感染的?
You said they picked up this disease from a beacon?

118
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,580
是赛昂人说的
According to the Cylons.

119
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:45,160
能得到病原体的话就好了
Always good to have the source of the pathogen.

120
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:47,000
你能把它给弄到卡拉狄加上吗?
Can you bring it aboard Galactica?

121
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:49,920
不 太危险了 要限制暴露的危险
No, too dangerous. I want to limit our exposure.

122
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,460
囚犯怎么样了?
What about the prisoners?

123
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:52,590
囚犯?
Prisoners?

124
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:54,590
他们体内的病毒要更高级一些
The disease is more advanced in their systems,

125
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:58,470
所以我有了点想法 看看接下来病情会如何发展
so it'll give me at least an idea of what to expect as it progresses.

126
00:09:58,550 --> 00:10:02,930
而且等他们死后 就能知道我们的人能活多久了
And when they die, it'll tell me how long our people have to live.

127
00:10:03,010 --> 00:10:04,180
有多少囚犯?
How many prisoners?

128
00:10:04,270 --> 00:10:05,810
你抓到多少个?
How many you got?

129
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:15,480
阿波罗 这是卡拉狄加 第一次检查
HELO: Apollo, Galactica. Alpha check.

130
00:10:15,570 --> 00:10:18,700
卡拉狄加 我们看到你们了 正在接近右舷机库
Galactica. We have you in visual range. Approaching starboard hangar.

131
00:10:20,870 --> 00:10:22,700
阿波罗  那是什么?
HELO: Apollo, what was that?

132
00:10:25,040 --> 00:10:28,000
基地之星释放出大量能量
GAETA: Massive energy discharge from the Baseship!

133
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:31,750
它爆炸了 长官
It exploded, sir.

134
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,880
阿波罗 这是卡拉狄加  你们大家都还好吧?
Apollo, Galactica. You all right out there?

135
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:36,960
嗯  没事  我们还在这儿
Yeah, affirmative. We're still here.

136
00:10:37,050 --> 00:10:38,260
发生什么了?
What the hell happened?

137
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:40,430
基地之星爆炸了 一定是自毁
Baseship exploded. Must've self-destructed.

138
00:10:40,510 --> 00:10:42,470
你们这些家伙真走运 能平安出来
You guys are lucky you got out when you did.

139
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:44,220
收到
Roger that.

140
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:16,340
我相信没什么问题
Nothing the matter, I trust?

141
00:11:16,420 --> 00:11:17,840
我们有些问题
We have some questions.

142
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:20,920
为了背叛我们  你计划了多久   盖尤斯?
How long have you planned to betray us, Gaius?

143
00:11:23,470 --> 00:11:24,890
有趣
Funny.

144
00:11:31,690 --> 00:11:33,350
你当然是在开玩笑了
You're joking, of course.

145
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:35,270
你这是对你自己不负责任了
You're only making this harder on yourself.

146
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:37,110
等一等
Wait a minute.

147
00:11:37,190 --> 00:11:41,200
我是非常非常合作的 自从我来了以后
I have been more than very accommodating since I arrived here.

148
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:44,110
我帮你们找到了莎伦的孩子
I helped you find Sharon's baby.

149
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,870
我还帮你们搞到了通往地球的地图
I've helped you with the map towards Earth.

150
00:11:45,950 --> 00:11:47,830
我们知道信标的事情了 盖尤斯
We know about the beacon, Gaius.

151
00:11:47,910 --> 00:11:51,750
你知道它在那儿的 你知道那里有致命的病毒
You knew it was out there. You knew it contained a deadly virus.

152
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:54,250
不 我不知道
No, I didn't. I didn't.

153
00:11:54,330 --> 00:11:57,170
是卡拉狄加发明了那种病毒吗?
Was the virus created by Galactica?

154
00:11:57,250 --> 00:12:00,210
自从你登船以后  你和他们联系过吗?
D'ANNA: Have you been in contact with them since you've been on onboard,

155
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:03,970
或者说 在那次新卡布里卡大撤退之前就开始计划了?
or did you plan this before the evacuation of New Caprica?

156
00:12:09,350 --> 00:12:12,980
这是一个很大的误解
This is a most profound misunderstanding.

157
00:12:13,060 --> 00:12:17,730
我和那个病毒或那个信标没一点关系
No. I had nothing to do with the virus or the beacon.

158
00:12:17,820 --> 00:12:22,530
没错 我在基地之星上确实看到了它
Yes. Yes, I did discover it on the Baseship

159
00:12:22,610 --> 00:12:26,070
我是应该把这个情况及时跟你们说的 但是我没有
and I should have told you about it sooner, and I didn't.

160
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:28,740
因为我想你们会把病毒和我…
Because I thought, you know, you'd try and link me, you know,

161
00:12:28,830 --> 00:12:31,790
联系起来 事实也是如此
to the virus, which is what is going on right now.

162
00:12:31,870 --> 00:12:33,410
我错了 那是个错误
I was wrong and it was a mistake,

163
00:12:33,500 --> 00:12:35,370
我完全承认我有责任
and I fully admit my responsibility.

164
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:36,750
再也不会有这种事情了
It will never happen again,

165
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:42,710
并且我希望你们接受我最真诚的歉意
and I hope you accept my most, you know, my most humble apology.

166
00:12:48,350 --> 00:12:53,350
