Somebody sneezed, maybe?

507
00:41:03,790 --> 00:41:07,210
是啊 因为有人忘了擦干自己的鼻子
Yeah, an entire race almost wiped out

508
00:41:07,290 --> 00:41:10,500
差点就能灭掉一整个种族
because someone forgot to wipe their nose.

509
00:41:19,140 --> 00:41:25,640
