to one reported over 3,000 years ago,

511
00:41:29,770 --> 00:41:33,360
大概在那个时候 我们的第13部落离开了科波
right around the time that the Thirteenth Colony left Kobol.

512
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:38,410
那个信标是去地球的一个路标
That beacon was a signpost to Earth.

513
